### Create User
POST {{api_url}}/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

{
  "lastName": "SEGUIN",
  "firstName": "Augustin",
  "birthdate": "1998-06-15",
  "codePostal": "75011",
  "email": "augustin.seguin@inetum.com",
